data.description: Welcome to this Amazing historic house in Mentor. This spacious Tudor house has over 5000 plus of square feet living space. The home has 2 new heating systems in 2022, 2 new hot water tanks in 2022, and 2 new central air systems in 2022. The attic has been sprayed insulation over the entire attic to increase efficiency in 2022. The front door opens to a Ballroom- now Family room, to spiral staircase to master bedroom library with hidden storage behind book case. The staircase from foyer leads to an upstairs office overlooking the backyard. This awesome house features 5 spacious bedrooms, 3 full baths (Upstairs), 2 half baths (main floor) and built-in-barbecue in the 4 season room. Remarkable woodwork and 4 season patio, 3 season patio and summer patio. The home is set just beyond a privacy wall that encloses the beautiful grounds, 2+ car garage with spiral staircase to lower additional storage area, beautiful garden and nature path. Enjoy the in ground cement pool with new tile in 2023 and storage building for all your summer pool equipment.
